### Project Title: **360° News Report & Government Feedback System**

My project is called **360° News Report & Government Feedback System**.

The application will have a modern and attractive **Home Page** with advanced UI/UX design, animations, dashboards, and innovative features. The system will include:

### User Management

* **Admin Login** (default administrator access)
* **User Registration**
* **User Login**
* User profile management

### News Scraping Module

* Users can paste any news article URL.
* The system will automatically scrape and extract the news content from the provided URL.
* Scraped news articles will be stored securely in the database.

### AI-Powered News Analysis

After scraping the news, the system will:

* Analyze the sentiment of the news.
* Classify the news as:

  * Positive
  * Negative
  * Neutral
* Generate detailed sentiment reports and analytics.

### Government Alert System

* If a news article contains harmful, sensitive, or socially impactful content that could negatively affect society, public safety, or public sentiment, the system will automatically generate an alert.
* These alerts will be sent to the government/admin dashboard for review and action.
* Priority levels (Low, Medium, High, Critical) can be assigned to alerts.

### Dashboard Features

#### Admin Dashboard

* View all users
* Manage users
* View scraped news records
* Monitor sentiment analysis reports
* Review government alerts
* Analytics and statistics
* News category management
* Export reports

#### User Dashboard

* Submit news URLs
* View scraping history
* View sentiment analysis results
* Track submitted reports
* Receive notifications

### Database Management

The system will maintain:

* User data
* News articles
* Sentiment analysis results
* Government alerts
* Activity logs
* Report history

### Advanced Features

* AI-powered sentiment analysis
* Fake news detection
* News categorization
* Real-time notifications
* Interactive charts and dashboards
* Search and filtering system
* Report generation (PDF/Excel)
* News trend analysis
* Government feedback tracking
* Audit logs and security monitoring

### Technology Stack (Suggested)

**Frontend**

* React.js / Next.js
* Tailwind CSS
* Framer Motion

**Backend**

* Node.js + Express.js
* Python (for AI/ML processing)

**Database**

* MongoDB or PostgreSQL

**AI & NLP**

* Hugging Face Transformers
* BERT/RoBERTa Models
* Sentiment Analysis APIs

**Web Scraping**

* BeautifulSoup
* Scrapy
* Puppeteer

### Project Objective

The main objective of this project is to create an intelligent platform that collects news from various sources, analyzes its sentiment, identifies potentially harmful or socially impactful news, and provides timely alerts and feedback to government authorities through a centralized monitoring system.

